revision.text: ==Turkish== ===Etymology=== From {{inh|tr|ota|یكیدن|tr=yeñiden}}, from {{m|und|*yaŋï-dan}} /{{m|und|*yaŋa-dan|t=again, anew}}, originally ablative of {{inh|tr|trk-pro|*yaŋï}} /{{m|trk-pro|*yaŋa|t=new}}. Cognate with {{cog|tt|яңадан}}, {{cog|ba|яңынан}}, {{cog|ky|жаңыдан}}, {{cog|kum|янгыдан}}, {{cog|uz|yangidan}}, {{cog|kk|жаңадан}}, etc. ===Adverb=== {{tr-adv}} # [[anew]] # [[again]]
